OL,3,C'Shocking' footage of driver applying
OL,4,Cmake-up as she drives along the M40
OL,6,FA driver has been caught putting on
OL,7,Fher make-up as she was driving along
OL,8,Fthe M40 in Warwickshire.
OL,10,FThe driver was just one of many unsafe
OL,11,Fdrivers who have been caught on camera
OL,12,Fby police patrolling in National
OL,13,FHighways' unmarked HGV cabs.
OL,15,FFootage released also shows a motorist
OL,16,Fsteering with his knees while tucking
OL,17,Finto fast food on the M6, as well as a
OL,18,Fdriver using her mobile phone and
OL,19,Flooking at her laptop.
