OL,6,FIt comes ahead of a multi-agency week
OL,7,Fof action which will target unsafe
OL,8,Fdrivers along the length of the M6.
OL,10,FFootage shows a motorist so focused on
OL,11,Fapplying her make-up that she doesn't
OL,12,Fnotice the police officers driving
OL,13,Falongside her.
OL,15,FWhen the officers in the National
OL,16,FHighways unmarked HGV cab beep the
OL,17,Fhorn she continues applying her
OL,18,Fmakeup, the car swerving as she
OL,19,Ffocuses on the mirror.
