OL,6,FFootage also shows the driver of an
OL,7,FAudi A3 seemingly scrolling through
OL,8,Fher messages, and at one point driving
OL,9,Fwith both hands off the wheel. The
OL,10,Fofficers then spot the driver "doing
OL,11,Fsomething" with her laptop next to her.
OL,13,FShe puts the phone down as police let
OL,14,Fher know they are there ` after
OL,15,Falerting their colleagues travelling
OL,16,Fbehind.
