OL,6,FThe HGV cabs are now being used as
OL,7,Fpart of a Week of Action on the M6,
OL,8,Ftaking place from Monday 3 June to
OL,9,FSunday 9 June, which aims to reduce
OL,10,Fthe number of incidents on the
OL,11,Fmotorway.
OL,13,FThe week-long campaign takes place
OL,14,Falong the length of the M6, the
OL,15,Flongest motorway in the country, and
OL,16,Fhas been labelled Operation Vertebrae.
OL,18,FNational Highways say the most common
OL,19,Foffences they deal with are drivers
OL,20,Fnot wearing a seatbelt (13,562) and
OL,21,Fusing a mobile phone (11,965).
