OL,6,F"However, those who continue to take
OL,7,Frisks such as using their mobile phone
OL,8,Fat the wheel or other things that mean
OL,9,Fthat their hands are off the wheel are
OL,10,Fputting themselves and others in
OL,11,Fdanger. The Week of Action aims to
OL,12,Fmake all of our roads safer by raising
OL,13,Fawareness and encouraging motorists to
OL,14,Fthink carefully about their driving.
OL,16,F"Meanwhile, thanks to our Tramline
OL,17,FHGVs, police have been able to put a
OL,18,Fstop to incidents of driving which
OL,19,Fcould have very easily resulted in
OL,20,Fserious harm on the road."
