OL,6,FInspector Si Paull, from Warwickshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "Our officers are very
OL,8,Fenthusiastic about taking part in
OL,9,Foperations using National Highways
OL,10,Fowned unmarked HGVs because it allows
OL,11,Fus to intercept drivers like these who
OL,12,Fdo not take driving seriously and
OL,13,Fcould so easily be involved in a
OL,14,Fserious or fatal collision.
OL,16,F"Our aim is to save lives and
OL,17,Funfortunately we are seeing too many
OL,18,Fdrivers showing total disregard for
OL,19,Ftheir own safety and that of other
OL,20,Froad users whilst driving at motorway
OL,21,Fspeeds.
