OL,6,F"Warwickshire Police and partners will
OL,7,Fbe running regular operations using
OL,8,Fthe National Highways HGV this year
OL,9,Fand whilst we always choose to educate
OL,10,Fdrivers first, due to the high stakes
OL,11,Finvolved in some driving offences,
OL,12,Fofficers will be robust in their
OL,13,Factions against the motorists
OL,14,Finvolved."
